Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we don't need to\Ntake a detour here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving and broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If only that rug were still safe...\NDamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Help me! The monster inside of me\Nis about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two personalities...\Nwithin Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that when you arrived\Nat the warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that Asian and the arsonist\Nwere already fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Asian noticed you and fled...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Miss Anna Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the culprit is\Nan extreme right-winger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned himself in, saying that\Nit was a fire to celebrate his people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your identification checks out,\Nso that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,May I leave, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The townspeople referred to\Nthe Asian as Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by her clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,do you suppose she was\Ntrying to prostitute herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,About Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, that's what\Nthe Turks called the Asian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But as soon as we told them that he\Nwas suspected of multiple homicides,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they all said that\Nthey didn't know who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I became your reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're safe, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You just suddenly disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Those kinds of clothes\Ndefinitely match you better...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That earlier look didn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, aren't you going to\Nhave dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just coffee is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You always pour five spoonfuls\Nof sugar into your coffee, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee isn't good if it isn't sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked pretty glum for someone\Ninterviewing to work for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that strange that I put a lot of\Nsugar in my coffee? Umm...Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a beautiful girl like you\Nworking at my shop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,would be excellent for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should smile a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of your beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work very hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an Italian restaurant\Nin a country town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go around to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put out the food from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry the food out\Nto the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Plates you've taken away are to be\Nplaced on the right side of the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The wine is here, and the glasses\Nare on this shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also wine above this counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Order slips are placed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The wine is above the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses are over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, I'm Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're not really the waitress\Nfor this place, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt, Anna is\Nwaiting tables here, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, get me a carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, I'll have a bolognese!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, could you get me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders for a carbonara\Nand a bolognese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Vongole and rigatoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The fettuccine’s also ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right–!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosso, how did you trick this cutie\Ninto working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't trick anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, I'll take you to a store\Nmuch better than this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay if you harm my poster girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, "Crybaby" Rosso is\Nsaying something courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, just the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he was at my house crying\Nwhile he was watching a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Another order of squid ink risotto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... "Summertime" is playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Summertime" is playing\Nin the classical movie theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great that Frankfurt has\Na lot of movie theaters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on TV recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man... It just makes me\Ncry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie takes place in\Nthe Italian town of Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Venice was a port city\Nin medieval Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called "the City of Water."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a town that was built\Non a tideland known as a lagoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are canals running\Nthroughout the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to show you Venice sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, have you ever gone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... And the soundtrack\Nis also good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've probably\Nheard its theme song before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we watch it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We still might be able to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It'll get late if we go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking off from work\Nevery afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's always slow\Naround this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to be nosy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you go every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...that's fine. You can do\Nwhat you like in your free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. At Mr. Venkel's shooting range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're going to\NVenkel's place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, have you ever shot a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at guns\Nmakes me tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Garlic, olive oil, parsley, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The flavors of the other things\Nyou put in have disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's not real pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything requires training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, you can take a bath now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that there were movies\Nlike this when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rosso, you always cried\Nwhen you watched movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...when I was young,\NI never had the time to watch movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate a lot of delicious things then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't remember\Nhow any of them tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know the taste of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The taste of sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked up on you after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappeared after her parents\Nwere murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A request?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of...having you teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find out about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A professor at my university's\Nlaw department was researching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ristorante Nino Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sacco-Milano Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sabatini Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You were called as a witness\Nfor all three of those cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And all three fell apart due to\Nlack of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that professor had\Nan interesting theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,According to his theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a professional hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An incredible first-class one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people\Ndo you think I killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was still a kid... Before I knew it;\NI was a member of an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole, extorted money, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I became a hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to eat well, as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same on that day as well.\NThe same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was noon at a cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how many I'd already\Nkilled by then or who my victim was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him in my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He had ordered a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And began putting sugar in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One spoonful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Two spoonfuls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three spoonfuls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Four spoonfuls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When he poured the fifth spoonful\Nof sugar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I could taste the coffee I always drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The man savored that coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I dropped my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it... That's why I couldn't\Nkill people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask me how to kill\Nduring the past six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Must you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Rosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to forget\Nthe taste of sugar.
